     Check for *note inf: 105. and *note nan: 106. values.

 -- Function: null p
     Check for null pointers.

 -- Function: applp x
 -- Function: listp x
 -- Function: listnp x
 -- Function: tuplep x
     Predicates to check for function applications, proper lists, list
     nodes and proper tuples. Note that *note listnp: 14f. only checks
